Denis Villeneuve Retrospective Web Poster

A hypothetical web poster for a retrospective of Denis Villeneuve. Morphing shapes and letter forms were used to suggest the revelatory elements in Villeneuve's films. The poster is coded in pure CSS and is fully interactive. Mouse -over different elements to activate the animations.

The poster functions at 1200px width.
